This is the area corresponding to the West Sea. The first, second and fourth maps are inspired from the [[Spring 2015 Event]]. The third map resembles [[Phase 1/World 4#/4-5|4-5]] but with different routing.<br>
'''There are no repair docks on this hexagon, it will be necessary to move to the adjacent ones to be able to repair ships.<br>'''
:Clearing the first map of this area (V4-1), alongside [[Kancolle Kai:Sandbox/Area 7#/V7-3|V7-3]] gives access to [[KanColle Kai:Sandbox/Area 5#/V5-1|V5-1]] ('''南方海域''').
:Clearing the first map of this area (V4-1), alongside [[Kancolle Kai:Sandbox/Area 5#/V5-4|V5-4]] gives access to [[KanColle Kai:Sandbox/Area 14#/V14-1|V14-1]] ('''FS海域''').

